				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/D%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%BAc-%C4%90%C3%A0o-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-mi%E1%BA%BFu-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%A1c-thi-nh%E1%BA%A5t-lu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-C-UBTiy85T5Hu3tZHJN54w">Dạ túc Đào Nương miếu nhân tác thi nhất luật - 夜宿陶娘廟因作詩一律</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/author-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/D%E1%BB%A5-ch%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%B3-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%E1%BB%8Bch-v%C4%83n/poem-j9Hfw5Qp2ojck3M3yZbHSw">Dụ chư tỳ tướng hịch văn - 諭諸裨將檄文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-B3gaZnYZj3Y7n162MsC6mQ">Trần Quốc Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-ch%C3%AD-ca/poem--A3qpFL2UYH8DOEkrBgXVg">Đồ chí ca - 圖誌歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/H%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-huynh-%C4%91%C4%83ng-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-uO6IjZuCUlOqbOXBMRXVgQ">Hạ đường huynh đăng tường - 賀堂兄登庠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Phi-Hi%E1%BB%83n/Ki%E1%BA%BFm-h%E1%BB%93-v%E1%BB%8Dng-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-iH7dVcbd3QxyJmcXjodckg">Kiếm hồ vọng dạ - 劍湖望夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Phi-Hi%E1%BB%83n/author-3Ibogrnw0L8Ef4XTrzHpJA">Đặng Phi Hiển</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ti%E1%BA%BFn-Vinh/Mi%E1%BB%85n-t%E1%BB%AD-t%C3%B4n-h%C3%A0nh-thi%E1%BB%87n-thi/poem-QZDImn3oV_pqZTvRL3Njng">Miễn tử tôn hành thiện thi - 勉子孫行善詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ti%E1%BA%BFn-Vinh/author-sugo-Anz9j12NZlMZQamjA">Vũ Tiến Vinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Th%E1%BA%A3o-th%C6%B0-h%C3%BD-th%C3%A0nh/poem-vzg_Uj6Nhe4yJctsauSlBw">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Thảo thư hý thành” - 奉和御製草書戲成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-d6YU4KPKjTplShZhxLPIUg">Vũ Dương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-z1mwQ4HIrHO__b1PQA2_xw">Thiếu niên hành kỳ 2 - 少年行其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%C6%B0-Giao/V%E1%BB%8B-Th%C3%A0nh-d%E1%BA%A1-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-FHlcBFMwtJfzMEsO2GpLwA">Vị Thành dạ vấn - 渭城夜問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%C6%B0-Giao/author-3uHRTiwV92r5b5vAz-cCMA">Phạm Như Giao</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-H%C6%B0ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-I1hPBqvi22dMgRrAtRG6Xg">Vịnh Hưng Đạo đại vương - 詠陳興道大王</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
